title: CO2_Emission
text: This graph shows the change in total CO2 emissions since measurements started. The TidyTuesday used is from 2024-05-21 and the data set comes from Carbon Majors.

title: Flights_per_Month
text: This line graphs shows the total number of flights on average in every month in 90 countries from 2010-2018. The TidyTuesday is from 2024-12-24 and the data set comes from WorldPop.
